settings.heading: How long will it take to rehouse my lens?
settings.description: Whether you already own the base lenses or are planning to assemble a set from scratch, you can send us a message to get a precise quote for the specific focal lengths you have in mind. We require full payment before rehousing begins, but a 25% non-refundable deposit will hold your place in line and we will contact you for the remaining balance when your set comes up in the queue.
